OL,3,CPSNI to 'routinely' release mugshots
OL,4,Cof criminals
OL,6,FMugshots of convicted criminals will
OL,7,Fbe 'routinely' released by the PSNI
OL,8,Funder new guidance.
OL,10,FImages of offenders who are sentenced
OL,11,Fto 12 months or more in prison will
OL,12,Fnow be considered for publication.
OL,14,FThe move - which police say is under
OL,15,Fperiodic review - has been welcomed by
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland's Commissioner
OL,17,FDesignate for victims of crime.
