OL,3,CPSNI to 'routinely' release mugshots
OL,4,Cof criminals
OL,6,FPolice confirmed that there is now "a
OL,7,Fclear decision-making rationale"
OL,8,Fsurrounding the release of images and
OL,9,Fguidance around was issued to officers
OL,10,Fand staff in November 2025.
OL,12,FUnder new guidance, an image of an
OL,13,Foffender who has been sentenced to 12
OL,14,Fmonths or more in custody, should be
OL,15,Froutinely considered for release.
OL,17,FThe release of each image will be
OL,18,Fconsidered on an individual basis by a
OL,19,Fsenior police officer.
